    items. Adds standardized margins inbetween other section groups.</Shw::Text::Body>

  <Hds::SideNav::Section as |S|>
    <S.Generic>
      Example 1: Add Title, Link / Item, or Generic content
    </S.Generic>
  </Hds::SideNav::Section>
  <Hds::SideNav::Section as |S|>
    <S.Generic>
      Example 2: Add Title, Link / Item, or Generic content
    </S.Generic>
  </Hds::SideNav::Section>

