  </Shw::Text::Body>

  <Hds::SideNav::Section as |S|>
    <S.Link @label="Dashboard" @icon="dashboard" @href="#" />
  </Hds::SideNav::Section>

  <Shw::Text::Body>
    Containing a title and multiple Links:
